<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.9">
<l>tuṇainilai maṟṟe makkō ruḷateṉṟi rātu toḻumiṉkaḷ toṇṭar tolaiya</l>
<l>vuṇamulai muṅko ṭutta vuravōḷa tāvi yukavuṇṭu veṇṇey maruvi</l>
<l>paṇaimulai yāyar māta ruralōṭu kaṭṭa vataṉōṭu mōṭi yaṭalcēr</l>
<l>iṇaimaru tiṟṟu vīḻa naṭaikaṟṟa teṟṟal viṉaipaṟṟa ṟukkum vitiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees, worship without wishing that there is another place of refuge for us.</l>
<l>The toddler who practiced walking</l>
<l rend="indent">so that linked marutu [trees] with powers fell breaking,</l>
<l>Running with a mortar when a full-breasted herder woman tied him to it</l>
<l rend="indent">when he crept up to the butter,</l>
<l>Having consumed the life of the strong woman, so that she perished,</l>
<l rend="indent">who once gave her breast to suck to kill [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">will cut away the bonds of karma, truly!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
